#. 最原クン！　<CLT=cltSTRONG>“思い出しライト”<CLT=cltNORMAL>を見つけたというのは
#. 本当ですか！？
msgctxt "0000 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"Shuichi! Is it true that you've found another\n"
"<CLT=cltSTRONG>Flashback Light<CLT=cltNORMAL>!?"
msgstr ""

#. もちろん…本当だよ。
msgctxt "0001 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Yes, it's true."
msgstr ""

#. では、王馬さんの言う事も本当だったんですね！
#. 逆に驚きです！
msgctxt "0002 | c03_003_010 | C011_Chaba"
msgid ""
"Wait, so Kokichi *wasn't* lying!\n"
"I'm stunned! Startled! Shocked!"
msgstr ""

#. ね？　本当だったでしょ？
#. これで針千本飲まなくてもいいねー。
msgctxt "0003 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"See? I told you I wasn't lying. Good thing too,\n"
"cuz I don't want my pants on fire."
msgstr ""

#. さっそく、どうするか話し合いたいところだけど、
#. まだ百田君が来てないね…
msgctxt "0004 | c03_003_010 | C012_Shiro"
msgid ""
"I want to start talking about what we're \n"
"going to do, but Kaito isn't here yet..."
msgstr ""

#. 魔姫もまだだよー！
msgctxt "0005 | c03_003_010 | C013_Yonag"
msgid "Maki's not here either!"
msgstr ""

#. あぁ、春川ちゃんは来ないよ。
#. だって、呼んでないもん。
msgctxt "0006 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "Oh, Maki's not coming. I didn't invite her."
msgstr ""

#. …え？　呼んでないの？
msgctxt "0007 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Huh? You didn't invite her?"
msgstr ""

#. あんな人殺しなんかの事よりさ、
#. 入間ちゃんとキー坊は４階のコンピュータルームを見た？
msgctxt "0008 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Forget about that killer. Hey Miu, Kee-boy, did\n"
"you guys see the computer room on the 4th floor?"
msgstr ""

#. あぁ？　コンピュータールームだぁ？
msgctxt "0009 | c03_003_010 | C014_Iruma"
msgid "Computer room, you say? Go onnnn..."
msgstr ""

#. あぁ、校舎４階に変わったコンピューターがあったんだ。
#. 後でちょっと調べてもらえない？
msgctxt "0010 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Yeah, there was a big computer on the 4th\n"
"floor. Would you take a look later?"
msgstr ""

#. キーボくんか入間さんなら、
#. あのコンピューターの事もわかるかもしれないでしょ？
msgctxt "0011 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"You or Keebo might know something\n"
"about it, right?"
msgstr ""

#. すみません、ボクはコンピューターには弱いんです。
msgctxt "0012 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid "I'm sorry. I'm not very computer savvy."
msgstr ""

#. あ、あぁ…そうなんだ…
#. それは意外だね…
msgctxt "0013 | c03_003_010 | C012_Shiro"
msgid "O-Oh... Is that so...? That's...unexpected."
msgstr ""

#. ねェ…前々から聞こうと思ってたんだけどサ、
#. キーボ君の才能ってなんなの？
msgctxt "0014 | c03_003_010 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"I have been meaning to ask, but...\n"
"Keebo, what *is* your talent, exactly?"
msgstr ""

#. それは…色々とできますよ。
msgctxt "0015 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid "Well...I can do all sorts of things."
msgstr ""

#. そうだ！　落語とか結構得意なんですよ！？
msgctxt "0016 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"Oh yes! I'm pretty good at one-man comedy\n"
"shows, if I do say so myself!"
msgstr ""

#. キー坊は存在自体が<CLT=cltSTRONG>“超高校級”<CLT=cltNORMAL>ってだけで、
#. 存在以外にはこれといった特技はないんだよ。
msgctxt "0017 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Kee-boy's existence is the only <CLT=cltSTRONG>Ultimate<CLT=cltNORMAL> thing\n"
"about him. Other than that, he's got no talent."
msgstr ""

#. だから、落語とか得意だって言いましたよね！
msgctxt "0018 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"I just told you I'm good at one-man comedy\n"
"shows!"
msgstr ""

#. で、よくわかんねーけど、
#. そのコンピューターを調べりゃあいいんだな？
msgctxt "0019 | c03_003_010 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"I don't really get it, but we just need to check\n"
"out this computer room, right?"
msgstr ""

#. けど、オレ様はそんじょそこらの機械じゃイカねーぞ？
#. ちゃんと、オレ様をイカせられる代物なんだろーな！
msgctxt "0020 | c03_003_010 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"But I'm not gonna come just for some computer.\n"
"It's gonna take way more than that!"
msgstr ""

#. ど、どうだろうね…
#. モノクマーズは凄いコンピューターだって言ってたけど…
msgctxt "0021 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Ah, well...\n"
"The Monokubs did say it was amazing..."
msgstr ""

#. よおっ！　待たせたな！
msgctxt "0022 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid "Hey! Thanks for waiting!"
msgstr ""

#. も、百田くん！　それに――
msgctxt "0023 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "K-Kaito! And..."
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0024 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. は、春川さんっ！？
#. なんで、春川さんも一緒なんですか！？
msgctxt "0025 | c03_003_010 | C011_Chaba"
msgid "M-Maki!? Why is Maki with you!?"
msgstr ""

#. 大事な<CLT=cltSTRONG>“思い出しライト”<CLT=cltNORMAL>の件なんだ。
#. みんなで話し合うのが当たり前だろ。
msgctxt "0026 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Well, this is about that <CLT=cltSTRONG>Flashback Light<CLT=cltNORMAL>,\n"
"so everyone should be here, yeah?"
msgstr ""

#. けど…人殺しを生業とする危険人物まで、
#. <CLT=cltSTRONG>“みんな”<CLT=cltNORMAL>に入れなくてもいいんじゃないの？
msgctxt "0027 | c03_003_010 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"But...when you say <CLT=cltSTRONG>\"everyone\"<CLT=cltNORMAL> do you \n"
"truly need to include a professional killer?"
msgstr ""

#. …やっぱ帰るよ。
msgctxt "0028 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "...I'm leaving."
msgstr ""

#. まぁ、待てって。
msgctxt "0029 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid "Wait, hold on a sec."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>と、百田くんは、
#. 出ていこうとする春川さんの腕を強く掴んだ。
msgctxt "0030 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Kaito gripped Maki's arm before\n"
"she could leave."
msgstr ""

#. て言うか、百田ちゃん…
#. 化けの皮を剥がすって言ってたのはどうなったの？
msgctxt "0031 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Kaito, didn't you say you wanted to take\n"
"down her mask or whatever?"
msgstr ""

#. おう、これから剥がしてやろうと思ってるぜ。
#. こいつから<CLT=cltSTRONG>“人殺し”<CLT=cltNORMAL>の化けの皮をな。
msgctxt "0032 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Yeah, I'm gonna take down \n"
"her mask as a <CLT=cltSTRONG>murderer<CLT=cltNORMAL>."
msgstr ""

#. …え？
msgctxt "0033 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "...What?"
msgstr ""

#. こんな弱そうな女が、
#. 平気で人を殺すような冷酷人間とは思えなくてよ。
msgctxt "0034 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"I just can't believe a girl like her is capable\n"
"of killing people in cold blood.."
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0035 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. あの…そもそも本当なんですか？
#. 春川さんは本当に<CLT=cltSTRONG>“超高校級の暗殺者”<CLT=cltNORMAL>なんですか？
msgctxt "0036 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"Um... Is it true? Are you really the <CLT=cltSTRONG>Ultimate\n"
"Assassin<CLT=cltNORMAL>, Maki?"
msgstr ""

#. キミは…人を殺した事があるんですか？
msgctxt "0037 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid "Have you...killed anyone before?"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0038 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. …あるよ。
msgctxt "0039 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "...Yes."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>や、やっぱり…そうなのか。
msgctxt "0040 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>Really...?"
msgstr ""

#. どうして…それを隠してたの？
msgctxt "0041 | c03_003_010 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "Why...you hide that?"
msgstr ""

#. ケッ、決まってんじゃねーか！
#. 正体がバレる前にここにいる連中をぶっ殺す為だ！
msgctxt "0042 | c03_003_010 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"Pfft! Isn't it obvious!? It's so she could kill us\n"
"all before we figured out her identity!"
msgstr ""

#. 違う…こうなるのが嫌だったからだよ。
msgctxt "0043 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"You're wrong... It's because I knew you guys\n"
"would react this way."
msgstr ""

#. …え？
msgctxt "0044 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "...What?"
msgstr ""

#. 私の<CLT=cltSTRONG>“超高校級”<CLT=cltNORMAL>の才能を知ったら、
#. みんなは今みたいに私を恐れる…
msgctxt "0045 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"When people learn my <CLT=cltSTRONG>Ultimate<CLT=cltNORMAL> talent, they get\n"
"the same fear in their eyes that you all have..."
msgstr ""

#. その恐怖が…いずれ敵意に変わる。
msgctxt "0046 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "Eventually...that fear will turn into hate."
msgstr ""

#. 自分が殺される前に私を殺そうとする人が
#. 必ず出てくる。
msgctxt "0047 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"And then someone will try to kill me because\n"
"they're afraid I'll kill them first."
msgstr ""

#. そ、そんな事は――
msgctxt "0048 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "That's not—"
msgstr ""

#. 絶対…そうに決まってる。
#. 今まで私の正体を知った人はいつもそうだったから。
msgctxt "0049 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"Whenever someone learns my real identity, they\n"
"try to kill me. It happens every time. Always."
msgstr ""

#. …い、いつも？
msgctxt "0050 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "...A-Always?"
msgstr ""

#. ふーん…春川ちゃんは今まで
#. かなり凄惨な世界に生きてきたんだね…
msgctxt "0051 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "Hmm... You've lived a pretty sad life, Maki."
msgstr ""

#. あぁ…可哀想に。
#. 同情しちゃうな。泣いちゃうな。
msgctxt "0052 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Oh...poor, poor Maki. I feel so sorry for you.\n"
"I think I'm about to cry..."
msgstr ""

#. キミはそんな経験のせいで、
#. 人間の命なんて軽いと思うようになったんだね！？
msgctxt "0053 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Because of everything you've been through,\n"
"human life has no value to you now, is that it!?"
msgstr ""

#. …暗殺者と殺人鬼を一緒にしてんじゃねーよ！
msgctxt "0054 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid "She's an assassin, not some murderous fiend!"
msgstr ""

#. こいつが人を殺したのは確かだとしても、
#. それを平気に思ってるかどうかは――
msgctxt "0055 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Even if she did kill someone, that doesn't \n"
"mean she thinks it's okay to—"
msgstr ""

#. ねぇ、そろそろ手を離してよ？
msgctxt "0056 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "Hey, can you let go of me now?"
msgstr ""

#. ん？　お、おぉ…
msgctxt "0057 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid "Hm? O-Oh..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>そこで、百田くんがようやく手を離すと、
#. 春川さんは大きなため息を吐きながら言った。
msgctxt "0058 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Kaito finally let go of her arm,\n"
"and Maki let out a sigh."
msgstr ""

#. 信じてもらえない事くらい…わかってた。
msgctxt "0059 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "I knew you wouldn't believe me..."
msgstr ""

#. だから…隠してたんだよ。
#. できる限り、顔を会わせないようにしてた。
msgctxt "0060 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"That's why I kept it a secret...and tried\n"
"to avoid you guys as much as I could."
msgstr ""

#. それなのに、お節介なヤツが、
#. 私を引っ張り出そうとするのがいけないんだよ。
msgctxt "0061 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"But someone who doesn't know how to\n"
"mind his business kept dragging me places."
msgstr ""

#. …あぁ？　オレの事か？
msgctxt "0062 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid "Huh? Are you talking about me?"
msgstr ""

#. でも、これだけは言っておく。
msgctxt "0063 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "However, I'll say this..."
msgstr ""

#. 私は誰かを殺したりするつもりなんてない。
#. ただし…誰も私を殺そうとしなければだけどね。
msgctxt "0064 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"I have no intention of killing any of you...\n"
"unless one of you tries to kill me first."
msgstr ""

#. て言っても…
#. どうせ信じてもらえないんだろうけどさ。
msgctxt "0065 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"Having said that...you probably won't\n"
"believe me anyway."
msgstr ""

#. だったら…せめて私には関わらないで。
#. 私もあんた達とはできるだけ関わらないようにするから。
msgctxt "0066 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"So...you guys mind your business, I'll mind\n"
"mine, and we'll all agree to avoid each other."
msgstr ""

#. お願いだから…私の事は無視して。
msgctxt "0067 | c03_003_010 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "Please...just pretend I'm not even here."
msgstr ""

#. 春川…さん…
msgctxt "0068 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Maki..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>途中までは脅し文句のようだったけど、
#. 最後の言葉は…どこか寂しそうでもあった。
msgctxt "0069 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>It started out as a threat, but the last\n"
"bit...seemed a little sad."
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0070 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. まったく、百田ちゃんは何を考えてるんだよ。
#. オレらの団結に水を差すような真似をしてさ。
msgctxt "0071 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Geez, Kaito. What were you thinking?\n"
"Are you trying to turn us against each other?"
msgstr ""

#. ねぇ、みんな！
#. 百田ちゃんにはガッカリだよね！？
msgctxt "0072 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"I think I speak for everyone when I say, we're\n"
"all disappointed in you! Right, guys!?"
msgstr ""

#. い、いや…そこまでは思わないけど…
msgctxt "0073 | c03_003_010 | C012_Shiro"
msgid "N-No... I wouldn't say that, but..."
msgstr ""

#. それより…そろそろ本題に入らない？
#. 僕らは<CLT=cltSTRONG>“思い出しライト”<CLT=cltNORMAL>の件で集まったんだよネ？
msgctxt "0074 | c03_003_010 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"Shall we finally get started? We've all gathered\n"
"here for the <CLT=cltSTRONG>Flashback Light<CLT=cltNORMAL>, yes?"
msgstr ""

#. ちなみに…みなさんはどうするか
#. もう決めていますか？
msgctxt "0075 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"Yes... So, have we all decided what we're\n"
"going to do?"
msgstr ""

#. もちろん、使うしかないじゃないですか！
#. 新しい事実がわかるかもしれないんですから！
msgctxt "0076 | c03_003_010 | C011_Chaba"
msgid ""
"Use it, of course! We might be able to\n"
"remember something new!"
msgstr ""

#. ウチらをここに閉じ込めた
#. <CLT=cltSTRONG>“超高校級狩り”<CLT=cltNORMAL>の正体じゃな…
msgctxt "0077 | c03_003_010 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Like the true purpose of the <CLT=cltSTRONG>Ultimate Hunt<CLT=cltNORMAL>..."
msgstr ""

#. いや…まだそいつらが僕達を閉じ込めたって
#. 決まった訳じゃないけど…
msgctxt "0078 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Well...we don't know for sure if it's got\n"
"anything to do with why we're trapped here..."
msgstr ""

#. 優柔不断なサル語を喋ってんじゃねーよ！
#. そいつらが黒幕でぶっ決まりだろ！
msgctxt "0079 | c03_003_010 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"Don't gimme that wishy-washy bullshit! \n"
"Of course it's got something to do with why!"
msgstr ""

#. ねぇ、言い争ってるより、
#. さっさと使ってみた方が早いんじゃない？
msgctxt "0080 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Hey, instead of arguing, it'd be way faster to\n"
"just use it, y'know?"
msgstr ""

#. そうだね…ちょっと不安だけど、
#. やってみるしかないよね。
msgctxt "0081 | c03_003_010 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "Yeah... Gonta worry, but we gotta do it."
msgstr ""

#. でもでもー、何を思い出しても、
#. 外に出たいなんて思っちゃダメだよー。
msgctxt "0082 | c03_003_010 | C013_Yonag"
msgid ""
"But but, no matter what we remember, you\n"
"can't think about wanting to leave this place."
msgstr ""

#. そんな風に考えたら…
msgctxt "0083 | c03_003_010 | C013_Yonag"
msgid "If you think like that..."
msgstr ""

#. 今までの繰り返しになっちゃうよー。
msgctxt "0084 | c03_003_010 | C013_Yonag"
msgid "We'll just be repeating ourselves."
msgstr ""

#. わ、わかってますよ！
#. あんな事を繰り返してたまるもんですか！
msgctxt "0085 | c03_003_010 | C011_Chaba"
msgid ""
"I-I know that! And we can't go around\n"
"repeating ourselves!"
msgstr ""

#. では、やってみるとしましょうか。
#. 最原クン、お願いします。
msgctxt "0086 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"Then let's give it a try.\n"
"Shuichi, go for it."
msgstr ""

#. うーん、ちょっとドキドキ。
#. アレ…地味に気持ち悪いんだもん。
msgctxt "0087 | c03_003_010 | C012_Shiro"
msgid ""
"Umm, I'm a little nervous...\n"
"I'm sort of...just plain nauseous."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>みんなの不安げな視線を浴びながら、
#. 僕は<CLT=cltSTRONG>“思い出しライト”<CLT=cltMIND>のスイッチを入れた。
msgctxt "0088 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Everyone turned their eyes to me,\n"
"and I flicked on the <CLT=cltSTRONG>Flashback Light<CLT=cltMIND>."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>すると、その瞬間だった。
#. またしても…
msgctxt "0089 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>And at that moment, once again..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>世界が――
msgctxt "0090 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>The world..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>歪んだ――
msgctxt "0091 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>...warped."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>意識が空白になって、
#. その空白の中に<CLT=cltSTRONG>“ある光景”<CLT=cltMIND>が流れ込んできた。
msgctxt "0092 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>My consciousness went white, and somewhere\n"
"in that whiteness, a <CLT=cltSTRONG>scene<CLT=cltMIND> played."
msgstr ""

#. 若くて才能ある子だったのに、
#. どうしてこんな事に…
msgctxt "0093 | c03_003_010 | chara_Hatena"
msgid ""
"They were so young and talented...\n"
"How could this happen?"
msgstr ""

#. 事故…だったらしいわね。
#. <CLT=cltSTRONG>“あの連中”<CLT=cltNORMAL>から逃げている最中の。
msgctxt "0094 | c03_003_010 | chara_Hatena"
msgid ""
"It looked like...an accident. \n"
"They were running away from <CLT=cltSTRONG>that group<CLT=cltNORMAL>."
msgstr ""

#. …ただの事故なのか？
#. 俺にはとてもそうは思えないよ。
msgctxt "0095 | c03_003_010 | chara_Hatena"
msgid ""
"...Was it really just an accident though?\n"
"I honestly can't believe that."
msgstr ""

#. …ッ！？
msgctxt "0096 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Ah!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>今のは…なんだ？
msgctxt "0097 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>What...was that?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>葬式…？
msgctxt "0098 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>A funeral?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>しかも…僕自身と…
msgctxt "0099 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>It...was mine..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>ここにいる…みんなの？
msgctxt "0100 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>It was everyone's here!"
msgstr ""

#. で、でも…どうして僕が…
#. 僕自身の葬式を――
msgctxt "0101 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Wh-Why? Why was I...\n"
"at my own funeral?"
msgstr ""

#. えっ！？　葬式って…最原君も！？
msgctxt "0102 | c03_003_010 | C012_Shiro"
msgid "What!? A funeral... You, too, Shuichi!?"
msgstr ""

#. どうやら…またみんな同じ記憶を思い出したようだネ。
msgctxt "0103 | c03_003_010 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"It would appear we all remembered \n"
"the same thing."
msgstr ""

#. だったら、教えろ！
#. あ、あれは…どういう事なんだよっ！？
msgctxt "0104 | c03_003_010 | C014_Iruma"
msgid "But what the fuck does it mean!?"
msgstr ""

#. どうして、オレ様がテメーらの葬式を見てるんだよっ！？
#. し、しかも…その中にはオレ様自身も…！
msgctxt "0105 | c03_003_010 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"Why was I watching your guys' funeral!?\n"
"A-And...why was I there, too!?"
msgstr ""

#. ど、どうなってんのぉ…？
#. あの葬式って…なんなのぉ…？
msgctxt "0106 | c03_003_010 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"Wh-What the hell is goin' on!?\n"
"What was the funeral...?"
msgstr ""

#. それが…思い出せるのはあの葬式の光景だけで、
#. それ以外がさっぱりで…
msgctxt "0107 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"But...the only thing I can remember is seeing\n"
"that funeral. Nothing else..."
msgstr ""

#. まさか…ゴン太達はもう死んじゃってるの！？
msgctxt "0108 | c03_003_010 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "Maybe we...already dead!?"
msgstr ""

#. あっはっはっはっはっはっは！
#. んな訳ねーだろ！
msgctxt "0109 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Ahahahahahaha!\n"
"No way!"
msgstr ""

#. まったく…あんまりバカらしいもんだから、
#. つい笑っちまったぜ。
msgctxt "0110 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Geez...this is so stupid, I couldn't help \n"
"but laugh."
msgstr ""

#. つーか…そもそも、
#. あれは葬式なんかの記憶じゃねーよ。
msgctxt "0111 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"I mean...there's no way that was our \n"
"memory of our funeral..."
msgstr ""

#. じゃあ…なんなの？
msgctxt "0112 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Then what was it?"
msgstr ""

#. おそらく…文化祭かなんかの記憶だ。
msgctxt "0113 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"It was probably...a memory of our school \n"
"festival or something."
msgstr ""

#. …文化祭？
msgctxt "0114 | c03_003_010 | C012_Shiro"
msgid "School festival?"
msgstr ""

#. つまり、今のは文化祭の出し物とか
#. 演劇とかの記憶って訳だ。
msgctxt "0115 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Yeah, it was probably a memory from a play \n"
"we did for the school festival or something."
msgstr ""

#. つーか、そんなモン、
#. ちっと考えてみりゃあわかる事じゃねーか。
msgctxt "0116 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"I mean, isn't it obvious if you just \n"
"think about it?"
msgstr ""

#. あの葬式が本物だとしたら、
#. オレらがこうして生きてる訳がねーんだからよ！
msgctxt "0117 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"If that funeral was real, there's no way \n"
"we'd still be alive!"
msgstr ""

#. んあー…確かにそうじゃな。
msgctxt "0118 | c03_003_010 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Nyeeeh...that's true."
msgstr ""

#. でも、転子達ってバラバラの高校ですよ？
#. どうして…一緒に文化祭なんてやってたんですか？
msgctxt "0119 | c03_003_010 | C011_Chaba"
msgid ""
"But aren't we all from different high schools?\n"
"Why would we have a school festival together?"
msgstr ""

#. そ、それは…
#. きっと、この後で何か思い出すんだろ。
msgctxt "0120 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Th-That's...we'll probably remember \n"
"something else about it later."
msgstr ""

#. とにかく、あれが本物の葬式な訳がねー！
#. それだけは間違いねーぜ！
msgctxt "0121 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Anyway, there's no way that funeral was real!\n"
"There's no mistaking that!"
msgstr ""

#. そうですね…論理的に考えれば、
#. それで間違いないはずです…
msgctxt "0122 | c03_003_010 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"You're right... If we think about it logically,\n"
"that's clearly out of the question..."
msgstr ""

#. そっか…良かった。
#. みんな死んじゃってるのかと思っちゃったよ。
msgctxt "0123 | c03_003_010 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid ""
"Okay...good. Gonta think everyone was\n"
"already dead."
msgstr ""

#. バカ言ってんじゃねーよ！
#. ご覧の通り、オレはピンピンしてるぜ！
msgctxt "0124 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Stop saying stupid stuff! Look at me, \n"
"I'm alive! Hale and hearty!"
msgstr ""

#. で、オレ様を見る度にビンビンか！？
msgctxt "0125 | c03_003_010 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"Hardy? Cuz you get a hard-on every time\n"
"you see me?"
msgstr ""

#. そう言えば、噂で聞いたのですが…
#. 男死はその日の朝にビンビン具合がわかるらしいですね？
msgctxt "0126 | c03_003_010 | C011_Chaba"
msgid ""
"Oh, I heard males can tell they're healthy by\n"
"how hard they get in the morning! Is that true!?"
msgstr ""

#. ちょっ…！　い、いきなりやめてよぉ…！
msgctxt "0127 | c03_003_010 | C014_Iruma"
msgid "Hey! St-Stay in your lane, bitch!"
msgstr ""

#. …他人の下ネタには弱いんだね。
msgctxt "0128 | c03_003_010 | C012_Shiro"
msgid "I'm not good with other people's dirty jokes..."
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0129 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. あーあ、期待はずれだな…
msgctxt "0130 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid "Aw maaan, what a disappointment..."
msgstr ""

#. えっ？　期待はずれ？
msgctxt "0131 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "A disappointment?"
msgstr ""

#. んあー…確かに今回の<CLT=cltSTRONG>“思い出しライト”<CLT=cltNORMAL>は
#. 期待外れじゃったな…
msgctxt "0132 | c03_003_010 | C009_Yumen"
msgid ""
"Nyeeeh...it's true. This <CLT=cltSTRONG>Flashback Light<CLT=cltNORMAL> was \n"
"a real letdown..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltSTRONG>“超高校級狩り”<CLT=cltNORMAL>の事もわからんかったし、
#. これでは手掛かりにはならんわい。
msgctxt "0133 | c03_003_010 | C009_Yumen"
msgid ""
"We didn't find out anything about the \n"
"<CLT=cltSTRONG>Ultimate Hunt<CLT=cltNORMAL>. Just some weird memory."
msgstr ""

#. …あぁ、まったくだぜ。
#. 期待はずれもいいところだぜ…
msgctxt "0134 | c03_003_010 | C001_Momot"
msgid "Yeah, seriously. Talk about a disappointment..."
msgstr ""

#. いや、期待はずれなのはそっちじゃなくて、
#. むしろ、みんなの方なんだけど…
msgctxt "0135 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"No, I'm not talking about the memory.\n"
"I'm talking about you guys..."
msgstr ""

#. …え？
msgctxt "0136 | c03_003_010 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

#. あ、ううん！　なんでもないよ！
#. 今のは嘘だから気にしないで！
msgctxt "0137 | c03_003_010 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Oh, no! It's nothing! I'm just lying again,\n"
"so don't worry about it!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>だったら、最初から
#. 余計な事を言わないで欲しいけど…
msgctxt "0138 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>I wish you wouldn't have said\n"
"anything in the first place..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>でも、そんな事より、
#. さっき思い出した<CLT=cltSTRONG>“葬式の記憶”<CLT=cltMIND>って…
msgctxt "0139 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>But more importantly, the\n"
"<CLT=cltSTRONG>memory of the funeral<CLT=cltMIND> we saw..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>本物の葬式の記憶じゃない…のか。
msgctxt "0140 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>It can't be a memory of a real funeral..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>本当に…それでいいんだっけ？
msgctxt "0141 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid "<CLT=cltMIND>We have to learn more about this..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>それを思い出せない僕にとっては、
#. いくら考えても答えの出ない疑問だけど…
msgctxt "0142 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>No matter how hard I think about it,\n"
"I can't wrap my head around it."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>その後、食堂で食事を済ませた僕らは、
#. いったん、それぞれ自分の個室へと戻っていった。
msgctxt "0143 | c03_003_010 | chara_Blank"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>After that experience, we ate a meal in\n"
"the dining hall and returned to our rooms."
msgstr ""
